org.yangcentral.yangkit.model.api.schema

Interface YangSchemaContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SchemaNodeContainer

    public interface YangSchemaContext
extends SchemaNodeContainer
    the interface of yang schema context. a schema context contains all yang modules including import-only yang modules. when a series of yang files are parsed to yang modules,these yang modules will be added to a yang schema context. user can validate the yang schema context by calling validate method.
    Since:
    7/8/2022
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    frank feng
